<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="since-adv">since <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪns/    美 /sɪns/  </p>
<p>[常与现在或过去完成时连用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>从那时以后；后来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have not seen him since.
从那以后，我就没见过他。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="ever-since">ever since</h3>
<p>1.<strong>从那时起直至今日；此后一直：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their work has influenced other writers ever since.
他们的作品自那时起一直影响着其他作家。</p><footer>外研③ – 1</footer></div></div>